description: The VAR_CONTAINED table contains the list of simple or complex variants contained within a complex variant.

columns.name: VARIANT_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the variant record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.description: The unique ID of the variant contained within this complex variant.
